📖 Instructions Welcome to the Budget Manager!
Use Form 1 to view your daily, monthly, or yearly budget overview.
Add income and expenses to track your finances.
Use the Load button to display saved data for a selected date.
To add or edit details, open Form 2.
🔑 Legend (Form 2)
Income → Enter your earnings (salary, bonuses, etc.).
Expense → Enter your spending (bills, food, transport, etc.).
Category → Select the type of income or expense.
Amount → Enter the value in your currency.
Notes → Add optional details about the entry.
Save Button → Saves your budget data for the chosen date.
